  "title": "Store Assistant (Mobile phone) - Basic + Allowance = High Gross/ AWS",
  "description": "<p><strong>Summary</strong></p><ul><li>Working hours: 11am-9pm</li><li>Location: Islandwide hiring (East/ West)</li><li>Salary package: Basic from $2600 + Store Incentive + AWS</li><li>Fulltime, young & energetic team, friendly working environment</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage daily retail operations, including cashiering, receiving deliveries, and maintaining store cleanliness and displays.</li><li>Provide excellent customer service by engaging walk-in customers, understanding their needs, and recommending suitable products and solutions.</li><li>Handle customer inquiries, resolve issues professionally, and provide after-sales support, including repair-related assistance.</li><li>Support the team with ad-hoc tasks as required to ensure smooth store operations.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Entry level are welcome to apply, training is provided.</li><li>Candidate with retail experience will have added advantage.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>To Apply, kindly click on the <strong>\"APPLY NOW\"</strong> button</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Boo Seng Hong (R25129172)</p>",
